{"type": "article", "id": 5116, "title": "口臭探测器 Mint", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-12T07:55:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233801A3vLDI1npwKPt0FY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自硅谷的呼吸分析技术团队 Breathometer ，日前推出一款可以随身携带的口臭探测器 Mint。如若想要摆脱口臭，用户只需要将其开口放进嘴里吹几秒钟，口臭就会消失地无影无踪。此外，他了摆脱口臭的功能，Mint 还能从呼吸中判断用户是否缺水，可以用来提醒用户每日摄取适当的水量。目前，Mint 正在 Indiegogo 上众筹，起售价 99 美元（约合人民币 614 元），<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/breathometer-mint-for-breath-quality-and-hydration\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，预计今年 8 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233759wJnhIcsvDFCaBfol.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338003FimxOHn1VTsQS8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233800n04cxyHG1udCzhkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233801FrU4pLixVj6zMt2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}